data.name: label5.Text
data.value: TO MODIFY OBJECT ATTRIBUTES, PLEASE ENSURE ALL INPUTS BELOW ARE PROPERLY FILLED IN. YOU NEED TO LOGIN WITH A VALID ADMINISTRATOR ACCOUNT, SELECT THE ATTRIBUTE MODIFICATIONS TO BE MADE AND SPECIFY THE FILE NAME FOR THE LOG FILE TO BE GENERATED. TO LOCATE THE OBJECTS WHOSE ATTRIBUTES YOU WANT TO MODIFY, ENTER YOUR SEARCH PARAMETERS IN THE OBJECT SEARCH INPUTS. HIT THE PROCESS BUTTON TO LAUNCH THE OPERATION.
